<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>س ط ر<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٥١٧ - س ط ر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سطَرَ يَسطُر، سَطْرًا، فهو ساطِر، والمفعول مَسْطور<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• سطَر الكتابَ:</span> كتَبَه <span class="c1">"سطَر الرسالةَ- <span class="c3">{وَالْقَلَمِ وَمَا يَسْطُرُونَ}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• سطَر الشَّيءَ:</span> صَفَّه <span class="c1">"سطَر السّيارات بجوار الرّصيف"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>